node.text: What’s up !!! It is FINALLY time to announce the project I have been working on over these last few months! I have created my very own fitness app called Demi Bagby Fit! So many of you ask about my training and how I have gotten to where I am today, sooooo I decided to show you just that! On the @demibagbyfit app releasing on my bday January 10 I will have my first ever workout program! This program is the training I do everyday 🤯 With a combination of body weight moments, weights, endurance, agility, and performance based training, I created a 12 week program for both men and women to get started on their fun fitness journies!!!! Reaching your fitness goals is about consistent hard work, and that comes from making strides every day. Always moving forward and working to become the best version of yourself! I am so beyond excited to share with you my passion for fitness in ways that can hopefully inspire you too! 💙 The full bts video of creating this app is on my YouTube - link in bio !!! I ALSO have a launch event for DBFit coming January 11 th in Santa Monica California ... text me to RSVP!!! ‭+1 (619) 332-1292‬ :) or just text me to say what’s up because now I have a # to be able to connect and chat with you all! AHHHH more updates coming soon!!! Love you all, let’s SEND IT!!! @demibagbyfit

node.text: I honestly can’t describe how much these photos mean to me. I had the most incredible time at Fort Knox with @goarmy training with the @usarmywarriorfit team and making new lifelong friends along the way. Through literal blood, sweat, and tears, I had the opportunity to challenge myself in new ways I’ve never experienced. I don’t think I’ve cried and laughed so hard in my life 🤣 From completing the Army Combat Fitness Test, to zipping around in razrs and singing probably the worst karaoke I’ve ever sang in my life… I got to see first hand how disciplined, courageous, hardworking, and fun the Army is 💚 checkout my recent yt vid of me attempting the Army ACFT and take a look at all the awesome jobs @goarmy has to offer! Let’s just say I definitely will not qualify for the band anytime soon 😜 butttt maybe the warrior fitness team will keep me 🥰 #ad

node.text: CANDID by Demi!!! 🥳 I am beyond frikin excited to announce the launch of my NEW clothing brand CANDID!! ✨ ya know ya girl is alllll about the vibesssss so I chose the name CANDID because I LOVE livin happily in the moment 🙌🏼 anddd it motivates me because it states I CAN and I DID!! 💪🏼 #PowerfullyPositive This is just the beginning of something so exciting and I can’t want to continue to share all my love with each and every one of you!! 💕 So yeah… Live CANDID, be authentically you, and don’t forget to smile!! Checkout my latest clothing release - link in bio - and have the best day ever!! 🤙🏼 #CANDID

node.text:
I challenged strangers to workout with me🔥💦 #PowerfullyPositive @demibagbyfit⁣
⁣
Nothing makes me more motivated than seeing people reach their training goals and havin fun while doing so! #PowerfullyPositive Making new friends and trying new things is what I live for!! I know I can’t train with all your amazing selves in person buttt come join my @demibagbyfit Vibe Tribe facebook community group so we can all challenge each other from wherever our happy lil feet are🤍 link in bio to join the group 🤗 What motivates you to keep working toward your goals?!⁣
⁣
Come train with me for $1 @demibagbyfit⁣
⁣
Wearing: @gymshark @gymsharkwomen
